	<Title>
		Chicken soup: Can it treat a cold?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Generations of parents have spooned chicken soup into their sick children. Researchers say that chicken soup may be soothing because of its possible anti-inflammatory and mucus-thinning properties.&lt;/p&gt;
